Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.41,0:00:08.95,Flashback,Kamome,0,0,0,,When I'm with you, I can go anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.95,0:00:10.85,Flashback,Suzume,0,0,0,,What're you singing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.85,0:00:11.67,Flashback,Kamome,0,0,0,,"With."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.67,0:00:13.01,Flashback,Suzume,0,0,0,,What's that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.63,0:00:16.34,Flashback,Tsubame,0,0,0,,As in, "to be together" in English.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.34,0:00:18.01,Flashback,Kamome,0,0,0,,It means to be together?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.01,0:00:20.67,Flashback,Taka,0,0,0,,You were singing it\Nand didn't even know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.78,0:00:24.69,Flashback,Suzume,0,0,0,,The title means "to be together"? Weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.69,0:00:28.56,Flashback,Hayato,0,0,0,,Speaking of titles for things,\Nshould we pick out a team name?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.97,0:00:30.07,Flashback,Taka,0,0,0,,A team name?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:33.84,Flashback,Kamome,0,0,0,,Oh, I already have one in mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.48,0:00:35.57,Flashback,Kamome,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.84,0:00:37.22,Flashback,Taka,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.22,0:00:39.41,Flashback,Kamome,0,0,0,,It's Higeneko, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.41,0:00:42.09,Flashback,Kamome,0,0,0,,So there, it's settled!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.09,0:00:45.94,Flashback,Kamome,0,0,0,,Our team name is Team Higeneko Kamome!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:47.42,Flashback,Taka,0,0,0,,Leave "Kamome" out!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.79,0:00:49.97,Flashback,Kamome,0,0,0,,Okay, then the Higenekos!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.97,0:00:51.13,Flashback,Kamome,0,0,0,,Whoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.13,0:00:52.74,Flashback,Suzume; Tsubame,0,0,0,,Whoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.78,0:00:55.51,Flashback,Taka; Hayato,0,0,0,,Wh-Whoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.94,0:00:57.64,Flashback,Taka,0,0,0,,Kamome!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.64,0:01:04.02,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,So heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.56,0:01:12.27,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Hey, get up, Kamome.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.30,0:01:18.78,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,He's gonna do naughty things to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.78,0:01:20.35,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I would never!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.97,0:02:54.61,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Food... check!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.38,0:02:59.03,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Camping gear we borrowed \Nfrom Ryouichi... check!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:01.47,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Attention, Takahara Hairi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.47,0:03:02.47,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:05.05,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Is your arm all better?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.42,0:03:06.29,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.72,0:03:07.89,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.89,0:03:08.88,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.88,0:03:12.88,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Then off we go on our adventure \Nto find the pirate ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:13.73,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.02,0:03:20.57,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,So, which way from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.03,0:03:22.64,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.61,0:03:24.87,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,That way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.58,0:03:38.46,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.89,0:03:49.47,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,So this is our starting point.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.47,0:03:50.71,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:03:59.24,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,"With," was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.24,0:04:01.77,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I remember hearing it a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.77,0:04:02.78,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.94,0:04:17.25,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Sorry I walk so slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.25,0:04:20.59,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,It can't be easy rolling \Nthat suitcase on the tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.59,0:04:22.42,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,It's not so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.42,0:04:25.80,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,I switched to mountain gear before I left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.26,0:04:28.13,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.60,0:04:29.60,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Want me to take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:30.79,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:32.10,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.10,0:04:33.14,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.01,0:04:34.90,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Let's keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:40.07,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,I used to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:44.61,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,I remember holding everyone up before too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.61,0:04:47.07,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,I've always walked slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:48.41,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:49.69,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.49,0:04:54.18,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,We can just take it easy \Nand reminisce about the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.20,0:04:56.66,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Hairi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.66,0:04:58.64,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,You're such a nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.64,0:05:01.04,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Seriously, cut that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.27,0:05:16.35,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,It's really here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.48,0:05:27.36,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,That note telling us to go toward snack time\N meant in the direction of 3 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.36,0:05:29.45,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,You're on fire, Hairi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.23,0:05:33.54,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Do you think the cave is along these tracks?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:35.58,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I sure hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:45.69,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,So hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.38,0:05:47.92,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.80,0:05:51.52,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Wanna take a break in the shade?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.99,0:05:56.02,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Kamome?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.23,0:05:58.35,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Kamome?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.22,0:06:02.35,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:04.71,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Kamome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.04,0:06:08.86,Flashback,Tsubame,0,0,0,,So hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:17.62,Flashback,Tsubame,0,0,0,,It sure is hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.67,0:06:22.61,Flashback,Suzume,0,0,0,,Hey, how far are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:26.71,Flashback,Hayato,0,0,0,,Kamome-kun! Could you hurry up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:32.60,Flashback,Kamome,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.60,0:06:35.40,Flashback,Kamome,0,0,0,,I'm gonna take in the scenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.40,0:06:37.05,Flashback,Kamome,0,0,0,,You guys go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:40.58,Flashback,Taka,0,0,0,,You sure that isn't weighing you down?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.58,0:06:41.62,Flashback,Taka,0,0,0,,I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.62,0:06:43.46,Flashback,Kamome,0,0,0,,No, I'll handle it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:46.45,Flashback,Taka,0,0,0,,Stop arguing and give it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.44,0:06:46.45,Flashback - Top,Kamome,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.45,0:06:49.03,Flashback,Taka,0,0,0,,Give it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.27,0:06:49.03,Flashback - Top,Kamome,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.31,0:06:53.99,Flashback,Taka,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.99,0:06:56.12,Flashback,Kamome,0,0,0,,I'll catch up later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.44,0:06:58.98,Flashback,Kamome,0,0,0,,I don't want to hold everyone back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:00.80,Flashback,Kamome,0,0,0,,Go on without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:02.12,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Hairi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:05.00,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Hey, Hairi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.00,0:07:06.18,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.18,0:07:08.60,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Takahara Hairi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.48,0:07:10.13,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.52,0:07:12.10,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.10,0:07:14.32,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,You were spaced out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:17.56,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Wait, where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.56,0:07:21.14,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,What? I was right behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:25.08,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.89,0:07:33.51,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,We've walked pretty far.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:37.41,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Do you think it's much farther?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.41,0:07:40.36,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Do you think we might have...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.07,0:07:43.28,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,The cave!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.42,0:07:47.25,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,The cave!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:49.35,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,We found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.35,0:07:50.30,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.20,0:08:03.94,Flashback,Taka,0,0,0,,So noisy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.03,0:08:10.58,Flashback,Kamome,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.21,0:08:13.95,Flashback,Taka,0,0,0,,Hey, you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.37,0:08:16.26,Flashback,Taka,0,0,0,,Does your leg hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.26,0:08:17.25,Flashback,Kamome,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:18.82,Flashback,Kamome,0,0,0,,I'm okay, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.82,0:08:20.08,Flashback,Kamome,0,0,0,,It'll get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.08,0:08:21.48,Flashback,Taka,0,0,0,,You're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:25.71,Flashback,Taka,0,0,0,,You've been in pain all day, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:29.78,Flashback,Taka,0,0,0,,You didn't want to give me the suitcase
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:32.33,Flashback,Taka,0,0,0,,'cause you're using it \Nlike a crutch, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.85,0:08:34.72,Flashback,Kamome,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.34,0:08:37.86,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.74,0:08:40.32,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.74,0:08:48.11,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,She's gonna do naughty things to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.93,0:08:50.40,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Am not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.40,0:08:52.40,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Anyway, did you get any rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.43,0:08:55.74,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.02,0:08:58.98,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Hey, can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.67,0:09:02.95,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,I managed to sleep, but I sweated a ton.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.95,0:09:04.33,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.33,0:09:05.21,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.21,0:09:10.45,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Well, there's a little \Nspring-looking thing over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.45,0:09:11.50,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:17.50,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,And, so, I was thinking \Nof going for a bit of a dip.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.47,0:09:33.60,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Oh, hey, splashing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.60,0:09:35.13,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Wonder what that could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.13,0:09:36.45,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Just kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:40.78,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.05,0:09:44.52,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Something's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.52,0:09:45.95,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Something huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.96,0:09:49.83,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,She's not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.83,0:09:51.46,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,They're {\i0}huge{\i1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.41,0:09:54.51,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,You saw what where?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.51,0:09:56.30,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,B-By those rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.42,0:10:03.50,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Maybe this is his watering hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.18,0:10:07.81,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Must've gotten excited after \Nseeing you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.06,0:10:09.20,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.20,0:10:12.02,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,He got excited because he saw me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:12.86,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:13.50,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.97,0:10:16.19,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Oh, no, I'm not talking about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:27.54,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,You didn't see, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.04,0:10:29.80,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,S-See what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.80,0:10:31.35,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.83,0:10:32.87,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.87,0:10:34.53,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.14,0:10:36.25,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I saw nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.25,0:10:37.84,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Y-You're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.47,0:10:42.47,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I did! I couldn't help \Ncatching a glimpse, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.67,0:10:45.85,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,What exactly did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:47.85,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.85,0:10:48.37,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Your b—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:49.04,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Bwuh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.18,0:10:53.19,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Here we go again! The mysterious "bwuh" tic!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.04,0:11:00.03,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I know it's a bit late now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.34,0:11:03.40,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,But isn't entering a restricted\N cave dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.40,0:11:04.28,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.28,0:11:08.14,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,But there's no sense worrying about that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:10.00,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,It's plenty sensible to be worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:12.39,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,I'm going even if I have to go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.39,0:11:13.46,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.46,0:11:14.90,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I knew you'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.98,0:11:19.37,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,It's just like before...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.37,0:11:20.12,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.12,0:11:21.68,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,What do you mean, just like before?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.68,0:11:23.76,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Ah, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.30,0:11:29.14,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,We just need to go straight, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.54,0:11:30.86,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,If I remember right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.86,0:11:36.02,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,There's a part that gets narrow \Nabout 300 meters from the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.24,0:11:41.11,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.11,0:11:42.90,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Yeah, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:47.20,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,It opens up past this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:51.30,Flashback,Kamome,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:53.50,Flashback,Kamome,0,0,0,,We can get through here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.70,0:11:56.67,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I'll go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.09,0:11:58.67,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.41,0:12:06.02,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Hang on...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.02,0:12:08.00,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Have I been here before?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.40,0:12:19.86,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Which way are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.20,0:12:21.06,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,That way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:24.05,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,There's a stream just up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:25.12,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:32.79,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Is your leg okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.79,0:12:34.33,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.33,0:12:37.21,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I was... just wondering.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:42.46,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Aren't you using that suitcase \Nbecause your leg's messed up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.41,0:12:44.85,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Wh-Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.85,0:12:47.62,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,I'm totally fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.62,0:12:52.11,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have come here if I had a bad leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.11,0:12:53.72,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.72,0:12:56.10,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,So why are you dragging that around, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.10,0:12:57.35,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,This thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.33,0:13:00.65,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,I'm not telling you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.65,0:13:02.64,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,No, I want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:05.70,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,We're on an adventure together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:07.70,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Adventuring is dangerous business.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.19,0:13:11.56,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,You put everyone at risk by keeping secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.45,0:13:17.22,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I mean, not that there's anyone \Nelse besides you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.22,0:13:18.96,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.21,0:13:20.74,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,The truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.74,0:13:26.90,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,My leg hurts sometimes, \Nespecially on cold nights and mornings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.90,0:13:28.34,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.34,0:13:30.80,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I never told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.22,0:13:35.35,Flashback,Kamome,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I never told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.81,0:13:37.42,Flashback,Taka,0,0,0,,You said you were hospitalized.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:38.81,Flashback,Taka,0,0,0,,Were you sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.81,0:13:39.60,Flashback,Kamome,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.01,0:13:43.53,Flashback,Kamome,0,0,0,,Most of the time, \Nit's just a little hard to walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.53,0:13:49.61,Flashback,Kamome,0,0,0,,Sometimes it gets difficult \Nto breathe or even move at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.07,0:13:51.77,Flashback,Taka,0,0,0,,You've gotta be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.77,0:13:52.62,Flashback,Taka,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.99,0:13:55.16,Flashback,Taka,0,0,0,,Why would you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.92,0:13:57.61,Flashback,Kamome,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.61,0:14:01.95,Flashback,Kamome,0,0,0,,I was feeling well, so I thought I'd be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.95,0:14:03.78,Flashback,Taka,0,0,0,,We're going home in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:04.75,Flashback,Kamome,0,0,0,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.75,0:14:06.49,Flashback,Taka,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:08.80,Flashback,Taka,0,0,0,,You seriously plan on going\Ninto the cave like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:10.33,Flashback,Kamome,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:16.01,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Please, just don't tell me we're going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.11,0:14:18.81,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I knew you'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.94,0:14:22.50,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Hey, we've come this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:24.36,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,No point turning back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.21,0:14:27.44,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.11,0:14:29.79,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Let's take a quick break.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.79,0:14:30.61,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.75,0:14:32.73,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.88,0:14:36.86,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Why did you come to this island, Hairi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.86,0:14:38.46,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Where's this coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.46,0:14:42.17,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Because I feel like you've been\Nprobing me this entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:43.37,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,It's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.37,0:14:44.54,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:47.24,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I told you I came to heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:49.54,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,So you're hurt, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.54,0:14:50.71,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.71,0:14:51.51,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.51,0:14:55.82,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Hey, why do I have to get into personal stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.82,0:14:57.30,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,I'm curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.30,0:14:58.76,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,No keeping secrets!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.76,0:15:00.45,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Damn it all...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.91,0:15:04.81,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I screwed up a team thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.62,0:15:22.40,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,You screwed up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:24.79,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Long story short, I let people down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.06,0:15:27.02,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,So then you ran away?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.02,0:15:29.23,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Ran away, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.73,0:15:31.68,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Yeah, you could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.18,0:15:34.02,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.02,0:15:36.90,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,So you let people down...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.90,0:15:40.82,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Even so, it's cool that they were \Ncounting on you in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.82,0:15:42.06,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.26,0:15:47.53,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,It really stings to disappoint people\Nwhen they expect a lot of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.53,0:15:48.86,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.86,0:15:52.72,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Being let down stings a lot too, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:54.07,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:15:56.07,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Couldn't you be a bit more sympathetic?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.42,0:15:57.81,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.81,0:15:58.86,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.86,0:16:00.80,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,I was talking about something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.80,0:16:02.78,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Not about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.63,0:16:06.63,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,There's something I'm \Nreally looking forward to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:15.30,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,I didn't think I was, but the closer I get to\Nthe goal, the more I realize how eager I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.30,0:16:16.28,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.28,0:16:17.97,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Meeting my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.95,0:16:22.60,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,The pirate ship should\N still be past this cave,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.60,0:16:26.15,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,and at least one of them \Nshould already be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.15,0:16:29.86,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,They should be waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.32,0:16:34.66,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,But to be honest, I don't \Nthink there's anyone there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.45,0:16:38.92,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,I've always been in poor health.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.92,0:16:41.51,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,I spent a lot of time in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.51,0:16:45.12,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,I don't have many memories \Nof playing during summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.12,0:16:48.94,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,That's why this one is so important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.70,0:16:53.04,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,But I know it wasn't\N like that for anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.57,0:16:57.95,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,It was just one of many \Nmemories from that summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:17:00.53,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,It's been buried and forgotten...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.08,0:17:05.14,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,But to me, it's my only treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,0:17:08.40,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,That's why I'm so obsessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.97,0:17:11.24,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.02,0:17:13.99,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Wanna get going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.97,0:17:22.07,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Just a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.83,0:17:23.91,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Your flashlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:27.03,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,I-It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.03,0:17:29.14,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,I have spare batteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.94,0:17:31.71,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Kamome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.17,0:17:35.44,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Kamome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.74,0:17:48.52,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Hairi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.29,0:17:52.27,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Hairi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.57,0:17:57.92,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Hairi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.92,0:17:59.35,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Please, Hairi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.98,0:18:01.06,Flashback,Kamome,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.06,0:18:03.81,Flashback,Kamome,0,0,0,,I'm sure we're almost at our goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.55,0:18:21.05,Flashback,Kamome,0,0,0,,When I'm with you, I can go anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.78,0:18:28.34,Flashback,Kamome,0,0,0,,Or I'm fine not going anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.94,0:18:37.74,Flashback,Kamome,0,0,0,,When I'm with you, \NI can go anywhere in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.74,0:18:44.60,Flashback,Kamome,0,0,0,,Or be fine not going!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.33,0:18:48.96,Flashback,Kamome,0,0,0,,I can go anywhere—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.96,0:18:49.91,Flashback,Taka,0,0,0,,Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.91,0:18:51.14,Flashback,Suzume,0,0,0,,It's the exit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.14,0:18:52.18,Flashback,Hairi,0,0,0,,We're out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.18,0:18:53.67,Flashback,Tsubame,0,0,0,,I can smell the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.34,0:18:55.45,Flashback,Taka,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.45,0:18:56.07,Flashback,Kamome,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.71,0:19:08.57,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Hairi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.57,0:19:09.68,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.56,0:19:11.43,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.87,0:19:12.85,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.85,0:19:14.96,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:16.73,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,There's no way I'd drown.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.22,0:19:19.09,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I'm on the swim team.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.74,0:19:22.05,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,You never told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:23.57,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.57,0:19:27.99,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Which means it was your swim\N team you let down, in that case.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.99,0:19:29.91,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,You didn't need to bring that up {\i1}now{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.91,0:19:31.49,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.49,0:19:32.58,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.58,0:19:34.34,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Sorry if I've got the wrong idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.30,0:19:39.61,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,But it felt like I was being \Nkissed before I woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.80,0:19:45.22,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Were you giving me mouth-to-mouth?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.84,0:19:48.58,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I-It was for first aid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:50.52,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,You don't need to be so shy about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.52,0:19:51.62,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:53.76,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,It was first aid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.23,0:19:57.52,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Hairi, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.99,0:19:59.92,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,There's light over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.74,0:20:04.41,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Does your leg hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.41,0:20:05.49,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.49,0:20:06.87,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Where's the suitcase?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.42,0:20:10.24,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,It fell into the water, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.66,0:20:12.16,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.46,0:20:14.74,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Do you need my shoulder?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.23,0:20:16.42,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,I'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.78,0:20:18.17,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,We're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.17,0:20:19.42,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,I wanna go without any help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.15,0:20:22.26,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.66,0:20:25.09,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,But let's take our time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.09,0:20:26.01,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.93,0:20:29.78,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,About what you were saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.31,0:20:33.84,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,About how everyone forgot those memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.47,0:20:37.46,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I think you have grandiose ideas\N about summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:43.21,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,It's not as easy to make great memories \Nover summer as you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.21,0:20:47.83,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Things like adventuring across\N an island to find a pirate ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.04,0:20:53.91,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I'm no kid anymore,\N and even I'm excited right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.34,0:20:55.52,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:20:58.92,Default,Kamome,0,0,0,,Will you remember everything \Nthat happened today, Hairi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.94,0:21:01.46,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I think I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.01,0:21:03.92,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I think I'll remember it forever.

